title: Antichamber OST FLAC
description:
Hello, since i did not find this great and amazing ost anywhere i decided to upload it myself, this is the full two albums in flac quality.
The songs range from 350-700+ kbps, hope that this is what you were looking for.
The music is atmospheric relaxing music that is simply amazing!

Check out this youtuber for gameplay-commentary-walkthrough-news and updates about video games:



Info taken from their page:

Music from the game Antichamber, 
composed by Siddhartha Barnhoorn. 

Artwork by David Hellman. 

"This soundtrack is a compilation of music from the game. Inside the game itself the music is made up of layers which crossfade into each other, creating an evolving piece of ambient music which never has the same elements / layers on top of each other. Evolving in texture the further you venture into the world of Antichamber..."
